just_use dsl_player.py

# label: EARLY
# role: parse + execute the older DSL (peel/park/extend/...)

Verb vocabulary: peel / park / extend / dissolve / home
(plus stubs for augment / swap / splice / restore). See
file docstring + `claude-steve/random008.md` for the full
grammar.

Distinct from the BFS-solver DSL (`bfs_solver.describe_move`).
The two coexist; `bfs_solver` outputs a different vocabulary
that `verbs.py` translates to UI primitives.

## Status

See `dsl_planner.claude` — kept around pending Steve's
decision on retiring the older pipeline.

